The paper discusses a system designed to accelerate linear algebra and machine learning computations in Apache Spark by offloading them to high-performance computing libraries. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Numerical Analysis (cs.NA), and Mathematical Software (cs.MS). Among these, cs.DC and cs.LG are the most likely categories, as the paper focuses on improving the performance of large-scale data analysis using distributed computing and machine learning techniques.
